== 制作 ==
2014年10月，据报道[[威尔·阿奈特|威尔·阿奈特]]将在[[克里斯·麦凯|克里斯·麦凯]]导演的2017年《乐高蝙蝠侠》外传电影中回归<ref name=THRBatmanSpinoffWorks>{{cite news|last1=Kit|first1=Borys|title='Lego Batman' Spinoff Movie in the Works at Warner Bros.|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lego-batman-spinoff-movie-works-738631?utm_source=twitter|accessdate=2014-10-11|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141012101922/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/lego-batman-spinoff-movie-works-738631?utm_source=twitter|archive-date=2014-10-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此前麦凯曾执导《[[樂高玩電影2|樂高玩電影2]]》，但该项目被推迟<ref>{{cite web|last1=Fleming Jr.|first1=Mike|title=Warner Bros Builds ‘Lego’ Sequel With Chris McKay Directing|url=http://deadline.com/2014/03/warner-bros-builds-lego-sequel-with-chris-mckay-directing-697712/|publisher=Deadline|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2014-03-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223210600/http://deadline.com/2014/03/warner-bros-builds-lego-sequel-with-chris-mckay-directing-697712/|archive-date=2017-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=THRBatmanSpinoffWorks />。2014年10月30日，澳大利亚动画工作室宣布正商讨接下来三部乐高电影的制作事宜，[[新南威尔士州|新南威尔士州]]政府将资助所有电影<ref>{{cite news|last1=Frater|first1=Patrick|title=Australia’s Animal Logic Poised to Produce Next Three ‘Lego’ Movies|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/australias-animal-logic-poised-to-produce-next-three-lego-movies-1201343218/|accessdate=2014-10-30|work=Variety|date=2014-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104012947/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/australias-animal-logic-poised-to-produce-next-three-lego-movies-1201343218/|archive-date=2014-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
